{"tid":1587520,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"咪再侮辱狗狗","createTime":"2019-09-22T12:18:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-22T12:19:04.000Z","uid":179578,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"d9f0a33a06a452d6252e6fdcfc745c8bded61cee","tid":1587520,"uid":179578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T12:18:39.000Z","msg":"要叫<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">老鼠</span></span></strong><br />\n過街老鼠 人見人憎 <br />\n<br />\n搞到全港十八區烏煙瘴氣 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n啲尖牙利爪仲抓到大量香港人傷曬<br />\n死老鼠/臭老鼠/坑渠老鼠/過街老鼠點嗌都得<br />\n<br />\n老鼠所到之處都搞到民不聊生 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咪再將老鼠做嘅衰嘢屈落狗狗度<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n全民齊嗌  一定要趕走老鼠 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rKRaPtX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrKRaPtX.jpg&h=d7799cb1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"63baa28098567290d7a65f8a194c0131659b9139","tid":1587520,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T12:19:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YY8gJwH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYY8gJwH.jpg&h=de149ef0&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}